name: r-exact
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "3.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-exact
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Exact_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/Exact/Exact_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d67f5c71b1209bea655d1e8d7530fa72359e0bcac25312551524501d0287e3cf

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rootsolve
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-rootsolve

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('Exact')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('Exact')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=Exact
  license: GPL-2.0-only
  summary: Performs unconditional exact tests and power calculations for 2x2 contingency tables.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
